node.text:
Everyone has to start somewhere 🤷‍♂️ and today is Juliette’s turn to learn how to handle the venomous snakes 🐍 of course never do this on your own ❌ only professionals should ever mess with venomous snakes 🙌 and in this case I’m starting Juliette out on her training in case of emergency 🚨 luckily we have amazing venomous ambassadors at the zoo that are friendly that make her first time easy 😃 but we do have a few others that even make me pretty nervous 😬 
.
.
.
#reptile #snake #venomous #learn #education #training #rattlesnake #gaboonviper #wildlife #animals #igtv #igtvchannel #video #insta #style

node.title: Handling Venomous Snakes for the First Time 😳

node.text:
This video you can see why I like to pull boxes out of the enclosure 🤷‍♂️ this girl wasn’t even letting me tho 😳 you can also see how they choose to defend their small space they feel comfortable in 😮 only problem is I can’t leave her there with those infertile 🥚 they would rot 🤢 and shed be grumpy until we took them away!
.
.
.

.

Hatching baby pythons is always exciting 🎉 but even more exciting when they’re so rare and look so incredible 😱 these snakes have all sorts of combined genes 🧬 found from the wild and selectively bred to make these amazing snakes 🐍 they look like no other pieds and almost look like leopards 🐆 they’re absolutely beautiful and can’t wait to watch them grow up 🙏
.
.
.

.
.
.

node.text:
Everyone has to start somewhere 🤷‍♂️ and today is Juliette’s turn to learn how to handle the venomous snakes 🐍 of course never do this on your own ❌ only professionals should ever mess with venomous snakes 🙌 and in this case I’m starting Juliette out on her training in case of emergency 🚨 luckily we have amazing venomous ambassadors at the zoo that are friendly that make her first time easy 😃 but we do have a few others that even make me pretty nervous 😬 
.
.
.
#reptile #snake #venomous #learn #education #training #rattlesnake #gaboonviper #wildlife #animals #igtv #igtvchannel #video #insta #style

.
